fields.name: PrincipalId
fields.description: The object ID of the service principal object for the managed identity that is used to grant role-based access to an Azure resource.

fields.name: TenantId
fields.description: A Globally Unique Identifier (GUID) that represents the Azure AD tenant where the resource is now a member.

fields.name: Type
fields.description: The identityType which can be either SystemAssigned, UserAssigned, 'SystemAssigned,UserAssigned' or None

fields.name: UserAssignedIdentities
fields.description: Gets or sets the user assigned identities.
